  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Operations Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Solar Marine</strong>, a dry bulk owner / operator specialized in dry bulk market. With a strong commitment to safety, sustainability, and innovation, we provide world-class services to our global clientele. Our fleet of state-of-the-art vessels and our experienced team are at the heart of everything we do, ensuring we deliver on our promises, day in and day out.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are seeking a highly motivated <strong>Operations Manager</strong> to join our expanding team here in Singapore:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Maintain the safety standards and procedures of the day-to-day operations of the vessels we are operating</li>\n  <li>Monitor and analyze shipping costs, identify opportunities for cost optimization, and implement effective strategies to enhance operational efficiency</li>\n  <li>Coordinating with the legal and insurance team to minimize risk and exposure</li>\n  <li>Acting as a liaison between management and chartering</li>\n  <li>Keep charterers and owners advised on all post-fixture activities to ensure relevant operational information is passed on timely</li>\n  <li>Liaise with clients on resolution processes for post-fixture issues</li>\n  <li>Handle post-fixture tasks such as freight invoices, demurrage/dispatch, and port disbursement accounts</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>At least 5 years of experience in dry bulk operations</li>\n  <li>Strong knowledge of commercial, technical and operational aspects of the industry</li>\n  <li>Understanding of the Far East &amp; South East Asia trade patterns</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>We invite suitable candidates to submit:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Complete overview of your background in the form of a comprehensive CV</li>\n  <li>Detailed employment history, including achievements</li>\n  <li>Education background</li>\n  <li>Recent business photograph</li>\n</ul>",
